quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  11,25,"Ni$ Nuzen ed Nuê i ugdud is: \"nek d aneddaô nnwen ipbegginen"
  11,26,"iwakken ur tâabdem siwa Öebbi. Nek ugaded aâaqeb fellawen, ass aqeôhan"
  11,27,"Nnan imvebbôen, wid ijehlen, seg ugdud is: \"keçç, $uône$, d amdan am nekwni. Nwala, d ôôdiyen nne$, kan, war ameyyez, i k ivefôen. Ur nwala s wacu i $ tifem. Xaîi, nêesb ikwen d ikeddaben"
  11,28,"Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Acu twalam ma ddi$ d ubeggen n Mass iw? Ifka yi d aêunu s$uôeS. Idreg fellawen. Day a t nêeppem fellawen, ma kunwi tugim t"
  11,29,"A yagdud iw! Ur awen ssuture$ ayla, ilmend is; taqdiât iw ar Öebbi kan. Ur ppara$, nek, wid iumnen. S tidep, ad mlilen d Mass nnsen. Maca, nek wala$ kwen d agdud ur nessin"
  11,30,"A yagdud iw! Acu ara yi isellken seg ufus n Öebbi, lemmer i ten rri$ akin, day ur d tesmektayem ara"
  11,31,"Ur awen qqaôe$: $uôi lexzayen n Öebbi. Ur ssine$ tabavnit. Ur qqaôe$: nek d lmelk. Ur qqaôe$ i wid êeqôent wallen nnwen: ur asen Ippak ara Öebbi lxiô, d awez$i. Yif akw Öebbi akken Iéôa, i illan deg iman nnsen. Mulac ad ili$ seg imednas"
  11,32,"Nnan: \"a Nuê! Ni$ tnamrev a$, tessugtev a$ anamer. Ihi, awi ya$ d ayen i $ tâahdev, ma tessawalev tidep"
  11,33,"Inna: \"d Öebbi kan ar awen t id Iawin, ma ihwa yaS. Kunwi ur tesfunnugem"
  11,34,"Xas b$i$ a kwen neûêe$, ur tesfaydayam seg wanûaê iw, ma Ib$a Öebbi a kwen Itlef. Neppa d Mass nnwen; tu$alin nnwen $uôeS"
  11,35,"Ne$ qqaôen: \"isnulfa t id\". Ini: \"ma snulfa$ t id, lbe$wv iw i yiri w. Nek, ur ppka$ di lbe$wv nnwen"